{"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/srcsim/issues/52/comments/36048711.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/srcsim/issues/52#comment-36048711"}}, "issue": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/srcsim/issues/52.json"}}, "type": "issue", "id": 52, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/srcsim.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/srcsim"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{c41021d9-0217-4628-999d-7f8d82f98dcb}ts=c_plus_plus"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "srcsim", "full_name": "osrf/srcsim", "uuid": "{c41021d9-0217-4628-999d-7f8d82f98dcb}"}, "title": "Missing hand frames"}, "content": {"raw": "The issue with the neck is the `controller_gains` in the `lowerNeckPitch` joint. Here's what I see in the urdf from the newest val-description deb:\n\n~~~\n  <joint name=\"lowerNeckPitch\" type=\"revolute\">\n    <origin rpy=\"0.0 0.0 0.0\" xyz=\"0.0203518 0.0 0.33845\"/>\n    <axis xyz=\"0 1 0\"/>\n    <parent link=\"torso\"/>\n    <child link=\"lowerNeckPitchLink\"/>\n    <limit effort=\"26\" lower=\"0\" upper=\"1.162\" velocity=\"5\"/>\n    <controller_gains Kd=\"0\" Ki=\"0\" Kp=\"150\"/>\n    <dynamics damping=\"10\" friction=\"0.0\"/>\n  </joint>\n~~~\n\nWith Kp=150 and damping=10, I thought it was fixed. I'm double-checking...", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>The issue with the neck is the <code>controller_gains</code> in the <code>lowerNeckPitch</code> joint. Here's what I see in the urdf from the newest val-description deb:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span>  <span class=\"nt\">&lt;joint</span> <span class=\"na\">name=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;lowerNeckPitch&quot;</span> <span class=\"na\">type=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;revolute&quot;</span><span class=\"nt\">&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"nt\">&lt;origin</span> <span class=\"na\">rpy=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;0.0 0.0 0.0&quot;</span> <span class=\"na\">xyz=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;0.0203518 0.0 0.33845&quot;</span><span class=\"nt\">/&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"nt\">&lt;axis</span> <span class=\"na\">xyz=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;0 1 0&quot;</span><span class=\"nt\">/&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"nt\">&lt;parent</span> <span class=\"na\">link=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;torso&quot;</span><span class=\"nt\">/&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"nt\">&lt;child</span> <span class=\"na\">link=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;lowerNeckPitchLink&quot;</span><span class=\"nt\">/&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"nt\">&lt;limit</span> <span class=\"na\">effort=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;26&quot;</span> <span class=\"na\">lower=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;0&quot;</span> <span class=\"na\">upper=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;1.162&quot;</span> <span class=\"na\">velocity=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;5&quot;</span><span class=\"nt\">/&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"nt\">&lt;controller_gains</span> <span class=\"na\">Kd=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;0&quot;</span> <span class=\"na\">Ki=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;0&quot;</span> <span class=\"na\">Kp=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;150&quot;</span><span class=\"nt\">/&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"nt\">&lt;dynamics</span> <span class=\"na\">damping=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;10&quot;</span> <span class=\"na\">friction=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;0.0&quot;</span><span class=\"nt\">/&gt;</span>\n  <span class=\"nt\">&lt;/joint&gt;</span>\n</pre></div>\n\n\n<p>With Kp=150 and damping=10, I thought it was fixed. I'm double-checking...</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2017-04-18T19:00:57.027552+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Steve Peters", "uuid": "{2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1fb4816dad9e68337d3096f750951f6cd=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.